Clean, beautiful beach
Feb 2020 • Friends
This is a Gold Coast-like beach. Vast, clean and beautiful. Lifeguards on duty and they were very attentive. You can hire canopies and lazy chairs here. They don’t allow picnics and food so the beach stays rubbish-free.
Written February 10, 2020
Karolina S
Sheffield, UK13 contributions
Nice beach for a relaxing day
Mar 2020
It's a nice, large beach. It was very quiet in March I'm guessing because of the corona virus but it was even better for us. There is nice cafes and shops across the busy road and a little beach bars where you can get refreshments. The beach was fairly clean as well which is a plus.
Written October 6, 2020
