Beautiful beach
Nov 2019 • Solo
I am lucky to be staying in a Hotel located in My Khe beach. It is a long, sandy beach where you can swim without any problem. There are many amenities, restaurants and cafeterias on the ledge. In the evening, I went for a long walk on my khe beach while admiring the sunset
Written January 19, 2020
Wood77
Los Angeles, CA1,931 contributions
Beautiful Beach
There are two seasons in Vietnam, hot and hotter. Cooling in the ocean around Da Nang is welcome relieve. This soft sand beach was soooooo long and can accommodate many, many people. Sparse crowd during day we visited. Didn’t see any lifeguards. Watch for riptides.
palawanismyhome
Palawan Island, Philippines24,563 contributions
a wonderful sandy beach
Dec 2022
It is unfortunate that we visited My Khe Beach in December so swimming was out of the question. However we enjoyed a stroll along the promenade and admired the beautiful sandy beach. By the beach there were many cafes and restaurants as well as a small temple and basket boats, but the sea was too rough to see any of them in the water.
Written December 31, 2022
Szonja P
Budapest, Hungary12 contributions
Dec 2019
We visited the beach in December and hardly anyone was at the beach. I loved that it was nearly empty and you could enjoy your time in peace unlike in the overcrowded European beaches. The beach was very very clean, no trash or seaweed in sight. The water was quite warm. White sandy beach.
